lead_paragraph: Brandon Stone edged closer to a second European Tour title with a fine 66 in the third round of the Alfred Dunhill Championship on Saturday to lead by three shots at Leopard Creek Country Club.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Solid Stone Extends Alfred Dunhill Championship Lead
